  "actual": "CONFIRMED \u2014 attractor is non-stationary. Rolling W100 LR mean drifts 2.59 Sharpe points (6.46\u21929.05), Spearman rho=0.861. CUSUM break at L-945..L-1107 (stat=1.986, p<0.05). Regime-conditional LR means: genesis 5.53, consolidation 8.01, maturation 8.68 (total drift 3.15). Within-regime beta near zero (0.01-0.21) \u2014 weak AR(1) within each regime. The quality oscillation S538b detected is real but SUPERIMPOSED on a rising attractor. Mean-reversion operates within each developmental phase, not across phases.",
  "diff": "Expected drift >0.5: actual drift 3.15 (6.3x larger than threshold). Surprising: (1) within-regime beta near zero means AR(1) dynamics are weak WITHIN each regime \u2014 the OU process is mostly regime identity, not within-regime reversion; (2) the S538b prediction of decline to 8.97 is wrong framing \u2014 the attractor itself may be rising, so decline is toward a MOVING target; (3) CUSUM break around L-1000 suggests a third developmental transition may be ongoing.",
